{
  "text": "Article by the reaction of acetophenones (1) with phenylhydrazine under acidic conditions. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] The aldehydes (4) were prepared as previously described [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] by a Vilsmeier\u2212Haack reaction of the imines (3). Reduction of the aldehydes (4) with NaBH 4 resulted in high yields of the corresponding alcohols (5), which were subsequently converted to the chlorides (6) by treatment with thionyl chloride in toluene at 115\u00b0C for 2 h.",
